= jwz_threading

This is jwz_threading, a library implementing the JWZ E-Mail threading 
algorithm as described by Jamie Zawinski (http://www.jwz.org/doc/threading.html).

= Requirements
Ruby 1.8.* (not yet tested on Ruby 1.9.*)

Only tested on OS X

= Documentation

The documentation is in RDoc format in the doc subdirectory.

= Install
...

= Status

This package is currently considered ALPHA and therefore considered to be 
changed heavily in the near future. I very much appreciate suggestions 
and comments. 

= Tests

All tests can be found in /spec directory. Using RSpec here.

